               <msContents defective="false">
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1" defective="false">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the donor; incipit of the text and of its sections; incipit of the articles; abbreviations referring to other works; Ethiopic numerals; elements of the punctuation signs. &#xD;
On the incipit page (fol. 4r), and on fols. 5r and 102rb, a few lines are rubricated alternating with black lines.</rubric>
